\c 1
\p 
\v 7 A Christian leader...truly he must not be an arrogant person, not quick-tempered, not a drunkard, not a fighter, not greedy for money.
\c 3
\p 
\v 14 Christians should learn how to think wisely and to work well all the time. They should not sit around aimlessly. 
